title: Apple Unveils New iPhone 15 with Advanced Camera Features
description: Apple Inc. unveiled the iPhone 15 with improved camera technology, longer battery life, and USB-C charging. The device will be available starting September 22.

title: Tesla Introduces Updated Autopilot with Enhanced Safety
description: Tesla announced the rollout of an updated Autopilot system featuring enhanced safety features and improved lane-keeping capabilities.

title: Microsoft Launches AI-Powered Copilot for Office 365
description: Microsoft introduced Copilot, an AI assistant integrated into Office 365 applications, designed to boost productivity through natural language commands.
